# `CLI11` reference-binding pattern** at hibp_search.
# cpp:36-58 — each `app.add_option(NAME, REF, HELP)`
# call takes a REFERENCE to the struct field where
# the parsed value will be written.  CLI11's
# template machinery deduces the target type from
# the reference type — `std::string&` binds string
